snippet.title: Kick the Boss - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/KickTheBoss
iOS: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kick-the-boss/id504656060?mt=8
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gamehivecorp.kicktheboss.android
Website: http://www.gamehive.com


Beat up your boss with this game! We know how stupid and mean they can be. Stand up for yourself, give them what they deserve. Bazooka right in the face! You can punch, burn, stab, slap, egg them and much more!!

Features
  ✪    Best stress-relief game
  ✪    30+ upgradable weapons (More Coming!)
  ✪    4 characters with hilarious expressions
  ✪    2 backgrounds
  ✪    Secret combos
  ✪    Fully physics simulated
